milestones.description: Grant Flower and Gavin Rennie's 150-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 104 between Burmester and Andy Flower
Hitesh Modi and Aasif Karim's 100-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 67 between Chudasama and Thomas Odoyo
Hitesh Modi and Joseph Angara's 15-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between Aasif Karim and Rajab Ali
Campbell has broken the record for most ODIs (29) as captain for ZIM, going past Andy Flower
Chudasama has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (15) for KENYA, going past Aasif Karim
Otieno has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (3) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Tariq Iqbal's 2
